Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.89,-1:59:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.89,-1:59:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.07,0:23:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映在眼中的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.08,0:23:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名為戰鬥的容身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「蒼穹之戰神」第19話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢 - 視線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡嗎？
